      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. POPPY'S DARLIN' turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.48) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Has ability and looks hard to stop. 3. MR. SPECKLE has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (23.29) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including two wins. Great chance to atone. 1. US AND THEM produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Gosford over 388m behind My Wee Lass (23.09) in a Grade 5. Can measure up this time. 2. CHUTZPAH will give backers a sight.\",\"runners\":[7,1,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
